<p rend="chapter">Paṭṭhānappakaraṇa-aṭṭhakathā</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Devātidevo <pb ed="M" n="0.0341" /><pb ed="V" n="0.0340" /> devānaṃ, devadānavapūjito,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Desayitvā pakaraṇaṃ, yamakaṃ suddhasaṃyamo.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Atthato dhammato ceva, gambhīrassātha tassa yaṃ,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Anantaraṃ mahāvīro, sattamaṃ isisattamo.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Paṭṭhānaṃ nāma nāmena, nāmarūpanirodhano,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Desesi atigambhīra-nayamaṇḍitadesanaṃ.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Idāni <pb ed="V" n="0.0341" /> tassa sampatto, yasmā saṃvaṇṇanākkamo,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Tasmā naṃ vaṇṇayissāmi, taṃ suṇātha samāhitāti.</p>
</body>
